  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main class="page">
      <p class="eyebrow">About Us</p>
      <h1>About Car Franchise</h1>
      <h2>Welcome to my CSE340 Final Class Project!</h2>
      
      <p class="lead">
        This website was created as part of my project for CSE340. The goal of this project is to show how much I have learned in the course, especially in web design and web development. Through this project, I practiced building a complete and useful website from planning to implementation.
      </p>

      <p class="lead">
        The website is designed for a car dealership and focuses on helping people find both new and used cars based on their convenience and budget. Users can explore different vehicles and choose options that match their preferred price range.
      </p>

      <p class="lead">
        This project also reflects my future career goals. I am passionate about web design and development, and I plan to continue improving my skills to become a professional developer. Building this site is one of the important steps in my learning journey.
      </p>

      <p class="lead">
        Thank you for visiting my project!
      </p>

      <p class="lead">
        We build a simple car dealership website using Node.js, Express, EJS, and PostgreSQL.
      </p>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
